{"ha9de7dceg28b7g4a50gb75bg0267abc311f9": ["Do you use every magical device that crosses your path absent caution, or was this an ill-conceived exception?", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\HAG_Hagspawn_RD_AfterResurrection_Laezel.html", "e963560c-83fd-09ff-df74-79b003506472"], "hff0499eeg4220g4b0bga2efg37917411ea91": ["It was a valuable lesson... even if Connor's dead now.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\HAG_Hagspawn_RD_AfterResurrection_Laezel.html", "af63456d-254e-36f1-bfde-fc70246502f9"], "h8756eb47gb3a4g4329ga94dg67ef99bbe295": ["He was already dead. You just pulled his corpse around like a puppet.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\HAG_Hagspawn_RD_AfterResurrection_Laezel.html", "5bd3beaa-08ab-3bfc-3895-1d4156798e1b"], "hc04b879cg2bfeg47e9gbbecg4655607f10e6": ["Well, at least we got a zombie out of it.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\HAG_Hagspawn_RD_AfterResurrection_Laezel.html", "f1c0d5d7-b5cf-b792-2aaa-d8e60129951c"], "h387ee747g93ccg4cd2g98ddg4b016a9fc01a": ["Most of the people we meet are little better than mindless corpses.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\HAG_Hagspawn_RD_AfterResurrection_Laezel.html", "0715d01d-1120-1ead-8417-f8aa016a20b5"], "h0046765cg7450g4f02g8f50g761ae998d518": ["I suppose this one is honest about its value.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\HAG_Hagspawn_RD_AfterResurrection_Laezel.html", "62ff2132-d659-5f19-d9b7-0df3fc2adf91"], "ha1f04070g3dd7g4604g9a78g4f0be987ca1e": ["I wanted to give Mayrina her husband back.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\HAG_Hagspawn_RD_AfterResurrection_Laezel.html", "53cd88d8-ac24-9c77-c06f-ee2d93df0e4c"], "ha4ed765ag34c3g4e62gbf2cgee8e665b1700": ["He's a half-rotten column of flesh.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\HAG_Hagspawn_RD_AfterResurrection_Laezel.html", "815a0343-8eab-5091-0b72-72e0d91c42ad"], "hc3de36d4g4990g47aag932bg90ce793e3bea": ["I assumed her standards were higher.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\HAG_Hagspawn_RD_AfterResurrection_Laezel.html", "d60dbc5c-c7bf-03c9-baa8-892596f32d38"], "hbce16a08g6706g442ag9401gfe8e1167928f": ["We had to do something to help her.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\HAG_Hagspawn_RD_AfterResurrection_Laezel.html", "3a469598-e76e-0a2b-700d-10bbd5058e45"], "hb52c7e85gc249g4afbga81ag7164b4e11ec7": ["No, we did not.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\HAG_Hagspawn_RD_AfterResurrection_Laezel.html", "dcbdf918-477d-4349-259d-0cee9e495b6d"], "h1bdd1be6g9142g4813gb9fbgb8827513bc81": ["You can't learn without experimenting.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\HAG_Hagspawn_RD_AfterResurrection_Laezel.html", "1d19043e-9c92-c2f9-6eea-c36aa2d96020"], "h3b4595ffgfbe5g4ac3ga6a6gfb23d8911dd4": ["I see. Warn me next time so I can give your 'experiments' a wide berth.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\HAG_Hagspawn_RD_AfterResurrection_Laezel.html", "26bd1cbc-959c-fd1d-45f3-eb03e0281fe0"]}